{"tid":2003644,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"攝反送中抗爭光影 路透社奪普立茲獎","createTime":"2020-05-06T03:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T03:16:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ac6a7c6db10b43b38f1ce1c9a5ecd0cbb75c082","tid":2003644,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:10:55.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200506/VJGIDHOIC3KYJLOSW7FS5OJTDA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200506%2FVJGIDHOIC3KYJLOSW7FS5OJTDA%2F&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRKQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=3194f06b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200506%2FVJGIDHOIC3KYJLOSW7FS5OJTDA%2F&h=4211a576\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200506/VJGIDHOIC3KYJLOSW7FS5OJTDA/</a><br />\n<br />\n攝反送中抗爭光影<br />\n路透社奪普立茲獎<br />\n<br />\n【傳媒奧斯卡】美國「新聞界奧斯卡」普立茲獎（The Pulitzer Prizes）前日公佈本年度得獎名單，路透社憑記錄去年香港反送中運動的圖輯榮獲「突發新聞圖片獎」。普立茲委員會讚揚展示港人抗議公民自由受侵犯及捍衞自治的圖輯「涉獵廣泛而予人啟迪」。<br />\n<br />\n圖輯由20張相片組成，除前線抗爭者與警察、「藍絲」衝突，亦不乏溫和示威。相片分別由11位攝影記者掌鏡，唯一香港................社會了解和關注」。<br />\n<br />\n蕭文超又稱「只是謹守崗位，記錄真相」，運動中不少港人「都承受了無法言喻的犧牲和傷痛，有些人甚至已不在....................會帶來一些改變」。他強調獎項絕非他一人功勞，感謝團隊所有戰友，又認為努力、盡責的同業也值得大眾肯定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200506/large/1588695422_624f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200506%2Flarge%2F1588695422_624f.gif&h=fd2c7ba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200506/large/1588695418_41f0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200506%2Flarge%2F1588695418_41f0.gif&h=c7a4a92e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200506/large/1588695419_186e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200506%2Flarge%2F1588695419_186e.gif&h=f8e44bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯一港代表：盼帶來改變<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：揭原住民社區零警執法 非牟利傳媒獲最高殊榮<br />\n<br />\n路透社總編輯阿德勒（Stephen Adler）指同僚出色地捕捉了示威規模，相片「美麗、縈繞、啟發人心且極之難忘」，為團隊自豪。去年路透社亦憑中美洲難民到美國闖關......................透社自2008年以來第八次獲普立茲獎。<br />\n<br />\n此外，路透社亦...................含了去年9月2日的獨家報道──行政長官林鄭月娥私下表示若可選擇「第一件事辭職」、12月13日追訪前線年輕示威者的＜革命101＞（Revolution 101）。普立茲委員會讚報道深入，詳述中國在運動背後操盤，窺探「會塑造下世紀」形態的年輕示威者心境。<br />\n<br />\n國際知名香港社運人士黃之鋒向路透社道賀，另「感謝前線手足的付出與承擔」，不然攝影師也不能記錄到港人在反送中運動的勇氣、智慧與抗爭精神，又謂「The world is watching」（世界正在注視）。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"34474f9c530b38481b3ec9d73949d9fbce2df0e6","tid":2003644,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:12:13.000Z","msg":"其實仲有張獅鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055e42b451c9d036141aa18220588d966fb8de7b","tid":2003644,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1063d38caca4c07aae98b7bd98d4ee1e45935361","tid":2003644,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:16:36.000Z","msg":"拉得<br />\n又copy全文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}